Plot Summery.
Set in the very near distant future, an elite squad of highly trained 
marines, led by commanding officer CAPTAIN BUKES are sent on a routine 
training exercise to a remote island the precise location of which no one 
knows and from which all communications are cut off dead. Accompanying them 
on the mission is tech head' SPECIALIST MILLS, a mysterious coder whose brain 
is interfaced with a computer. What the unit soon discover when they reach 
the island is that the exercise is far from routine - they become live 
targets of terrifyingly advanced military robots and that MILLS is somehow 
involved in the conspiracy. But they also know that they need MILLS 
technology to survive the brutal situation that they find themselves in. 
Cut off and facing certain death the marines must fight for their lives 
to survive. And at the same time they must work out who and what MILLS 
really is and whose side is she really on.
